                         OPeNDAP Web Coverage Service

.............................................................................


Here you (should) have the Web Archive (war) file containing the OPeNDAP
Web Coverage Service (WCS).

To install the WCS:

1) Get and install Apache Tomcat 6.x (or newer - your milage may vary) from:

        http://tomcat.apache.org.


2) Place the "WCS.war" file in the directory $TOMCAT_HOME/webapps.


3) Start the Tomcat server.


4) Point your favorite web browser at:

        http://the.machine.on.which.you.are.running.tomcat:8080/WCS/

   in order to see the default presentation page for the WCS.


5) Find additional instructions and information here:

       http://docs.opendap.org/index.php/WCS_Service_version_1.1

